### Team Productivity
- **Development velocity** - Features delivered per sprint
- **Code quality** - Bug rates and technical debt
- **Review efficiency** - Time spent on code reviews
- **Documentation quality** - Completeness and accuracy
- **Team satisfaction** - Feedback on development experience

### AI Effectiveness
- **Suggestion acceptance rate** - Quality of AI recommendations
- **Time savings** - Reduced manual tasks and reviews
- **Quality improvements** - Measurable quality enhancements
- **Learning progress** - AI adaptation to team patterns
- **Team adoption** - Regular use of AI assistance

## Troubleshooting AI Assistance

### Common Issues
- **Over-suggestions** - Too many AI recommendations
- **Irrelevant suggestions** - AI not understanding context
- **Performance impact** - AI slowing down development
- **Learning problems** - AI not adapting to team preferences
- **Integration issues** - AI not working with existing tools

### Solutions
- **Adjust sensitivity** - Fine-tune AI activation triggers
- **Improve context** - Better project and team information
- **Optimize performance** - Streamline AI operations
- **Enhance learning** - Provide better feedback and examples
- **Fix integrations** - Resolve tool compatibility issues

